SUBDIRECTORY dynamic

The examples in this subdirectory are those used to demonstrate the use
of KERNEL.RUN in the Low Level Programming chapter of the user manual.

runcode.inc	PROTOCOL definition for runcode.occ
runcode.occ	Receive code down a channel; then execute it
callprog.occ	Call a complicated program with parameters

The runcode example can be compiled as follows

	oc runcode.occ

This callprog example can be built using imakef as follows

	imakef callprog.bah	
	make -f callprog.mak

When using an MS-DOS or VMS system, replace '-' by '/'
